msgstr "‘*That* self of which you speak does exist, I don’t deny it. "

msgctxt "dn1:3.11.3"
msgid "no ca kho, bho, ayaṃ attā ettāvatā sammā samucchinno hoti. "
msgstr "But that’s not how *this* self becomes rightly annihilated. "

msgctxt "dn1:3.11.4"
msgid "Atthi kho, bho, añño attā dibbo rūpī kāmāvacaro kabaḷīkārāhārabhakkho. "
msgstr "There is another self that is divine, physical, sensual, consuming solid food. "

msgctxt "dn1:3.11.5"
msgid "Taṃ tvaṃ na jānāsi na passasi. "
msgstr "You don’t know or see that. "

msgctxt "dn1:3.11.6"
msgid "Tamahaṃ jānāmi passāmi. "
msgstr "But I know it and see it. "

